## 🔄 Validation Workflow

```text
Founder Idea
      │
      ▼
Idea Discovery Chat
      │
      ▼
Context Collection
      │
      ▼
Parallel Agent Execution
      │
      ├── Market Analysis
      ├── Competitor Analysis
      ├── User Pain Points
      ├── Risk Assessment
      └── VC Mapping
      │
      ▼
Startup Intelligence Dashboard
      │
      ▼
Export Startup Report
```

